\c 1
\s Kwaziso
\p
\v 1 Pauro muapositori waKristu Jesu nekuda kwechido chaMwari, naTimotio hama,
\v 2 kuvatsvene nehama dzakatendeka muna Kristu vari paKorose: Nyasha kwamuri, nerugare rwunobva kuna Mwari Baba vedu naIshe Jesu Kristu.
\s Kuvonga kwaPauro pamusoro pavo
\p
\v 3 Tinopa kuvonga kuna Mwari naBaba vaIshe wedu Jesu Kristu, tichikunyengetererai nguva dzose,
\v 4 sezvo takanzwa zverutendo rwenyu muna Kristu Jesu, uye zverudo kuvatsvene vose,
\v 5 nekuda kwetariro yakagadzirirwa imwi kumatenga, yamakagara manzwa pashoko rechokwadi cheevhangeri,
\v 6 iyo yasvika kwamuri sepanyika yosewo; ichibereka chibereko, sezva\add inoita\add*wo kwamuri, kubvira pazuva ramakanzwa nekuziva nyasha dzaMwari muchokwadi;
\v 7 sezvamakadzidzawo kuna Epafrasi, muranda unodikanwa pamwe nesu, mushumiri wakatendeka waKristu nekuda kwenyu,
\v 8 iye wakatiudzawo \add zve\add*rudo rwenyu muMweya.
\s Pauro unovanyengeterera
\p
\v 9 Nekuda kweizvi isuwo, kubvira pazuva ratakanzwa, hatimiri kukunyengetererai, nekukumbira kuti muzadzwe neruzivo rwechido chake, pauchenjeri hwose nekunzwisisa kwemweya;
\v 10 kuti mufambe sezvinofanira Ishe muchimufadza pazvose, muchibereka zvibereko pabasa rose rakanaka, muchikura paruzivo rwaMwari;
\v 11 muchisimbiswa nesimba rose, zvichienderana nesimba rekurumbidzwa kwake, muve nemoyo murefu nekutsungirira nemufaro;
\v 12 muchipa kuvonga kuna Baba, vakatiita kuti tifanire kugoverana kwenhaka yevatsvene muchiedza.
\v 13 vakatinunura pasimba rerima, vakatishandurira muushe hweMwanakomana werudo rwavo,
\v 14 watine dzikinuro maari kubudikidza neropa rake, \add ndiko\add* kukanganwirwa kwezvivi.
\v 15 Ndiye mufananidzo waMwari usingaonekwi, dangwe rechisikwa choga choga;
\v 16 Nekuti maari zvinhu zvose zvakasikwa, zviri kumatenga nezviri panyika, zvinoonekwa nezvisingaonekwi, kana zviri zvigaro zveushe kana ushe, kana ukuru, kana masimba; zvinhu zvose zvakasikwa naye, \add zvikasikirwa \add*iye.
\v 17 Ndiye unotangira zvinhu zvose, uye zvinhu zvose zvakabatanidzwa maari.
\v 18 Uye ndiye musoro wemuviri, kereke; unova kutanga, dangwe kune vakafa; kuti pazvose iye ave wokutanga.
\v 19 Nekuti zvakafadza \add Baba\add*, kuti kuzara kose kugare maari,
\v 20 uye akonzere naye kuti zvinhu zvose zviyananiswe kwaari, amboita rugare kubudikidza neropa remuchinjikwa wake kubudikidza naiye, kunyange zviri panyika kunyange zviri kumatenga.
\v 21 Nemwi maimbova vaeni nevavengi mufungwa nemabasa akaipa, asi zvino wayanana \add nemwi\add*
\v 22 mumuviri wenyama yake kubudikidza nekufa akukumikidzei muri vatsvene, uye musina mhosva uye musingamhuriki pachiso chake,
\v 23 kana muchirambira parutendo makateyiwa uye makasimbiswa, uye hamubviswi patariro yeevhangeri yamakanzwa, yakaparidzirwa chisikwa choga choga chiri pasi pedenga; iyo yandakaitwa mushumiri wayo ini Pauro.
\s Kutambudzika kwaPauro pamusoro pavo
\p
\v 24 Zvino ndinofara pamatambudziko angu nekuda kwenyu, nekuzadzisa zvakasara pamatambudziko aKristu munyama yangu nekuda kwemuviri wake, inova kereke;
\v 25 iyo ini yandakaitwa mushumiri wayo zvichienderana nekuita kwaMwari kwandakapiwa pamusoro penyu, kuzadzisa shoko raMwari,
\v 26 chakavanzika chakange chakafukidzwa kubvira kare, nekubva kumazera, asi zvino chinoratidzwa kuvatsvene vake,
\v 27 kuna ivo Mwari vaakada kuzivisa kiti fuma yekubwinya kwechakavanzika ichi pakati pevahedheni chii, chinova Kristu mamuri, tariro yekubwinya;
\v 28 watinoparidza isu, tichiyambira munhu umwe neumwe, nekudzidzisa munhu umwe neumwe munjere dzose, kuti tikumikidze munhu umwe neumwe akakwana muna Kristu;
\v 29 ndizvo zvandinoshingairirawo, ndichirwa zvinoenderana nekubata kwake kunobata mandiri nesimba.
